translate spanish entry_discussion_992fe641:

    # Z "In the right situation, its an easier life than having to struggle for survival on their own, like you do."
    Z "En la situación correcta, es una vida más fácil que tener que luchar por sobrevivir por su cuenta, como tú haces."

# game/scripts/computer.rpy:369
translate spanish entry_discussion_b1123e3c:

    # I "You would have kept me locked up because I am different?"
