    # game/scripts/computer.rpy:391
    old "\nI have, once again, followed my gut instinct and I have led him to the Bunker. It's a huge gamble, but one that seems to be paying off. I think he might just be able to talk some sense into Fangs.\n\n\n"
    new "\nUna vez más, he seguido mi instinto y le he llevado al Búnker. Es una gran apuesta, pero que parece estar dando sus frutos. Creo que podría hacer entrar en razón a Fangs.\n\n\n"
